到都唔會有咩事，又唔係淡水魚。驚都驚三文魚啦。而且驗到又冇話條蟲係生定死，咁食菜同生果都好多見唔到嘅蟲。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />難分真與假"},{"pid":"29f02a828fc866f27e3141fca8c4bfbeb2f30fc5","tid":1123880,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:24:16.000Z","msg":"老老實實，我平時大灣區食開鯇魚刺身，唔係好信得過吞拿魚"},{"pid":"c77aa157ffd9c88e8969197544c81e73f373aeb0","tid":1123880,"uid":36383,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7bf1853e138b03ffd0ce15c55838993b75d8bd26","tid":1123880,"uid":135445,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c3e39dcdcc95111c68ed07ee77ce4cfabc2dc0d0","tid":1123880,"uid":36383,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c90a50390243e95d91ec25d0d599e09490463a4f","tid":1123880,"uid":142532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:21:40.000Z","msg":"今日都食咗 唔食吞拿魚ok嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:23:11.000Z","msg":"用下常識，呢啲魚嘅寄生蟲唔會係人體留得耐。食到都唔會有咩事，又唔係淡水魚。驚都驚三文魚啦。而且驗到又冇話條蟲係生定死，咁食菜同生果都好多見唔到嘅蟲。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />難分真與假"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:25:03.000Z","msg":"啱唔啱先，蟲又點。以前啲人食禾蟲，法國人食蝸牛。Bear Grylls 係人在野節目咪又咁食。"},{"pid":"47c7de752bf2f71b47e91320eebc45f6c605e2f7","tid":1123880,"uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:26:19.000Z","msg":"我只會將所謂寄生蟲當係蛋白質 supplement ，做 gym 嘅食多啲都唔怕。"},{"pid":"7a54b4c5d4c52d9b171bb56ef5ba4a2d292c191e","tid":1123880,"uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"元氣連鎖店，入咁多貨，其中 1% 有問題都好易驗到。但其他店細型，1% 有問題你未必驗到。驗到冇蟲都唔代表安全，驗都係 sampling 咁驗，所以咁都唔可以 conclude 啲乜嘢。<br />\n<br />\n我讀咁多年 econ 最大得著係 risk neutral 。抱住呢個心態，食都食得開心啲。"},{"pid":"1b2d557b59a94e6dc4505db3790e3b1fed97dcad","tid":1123880,"uid":194606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:56:26.000Z","msg":"好似好理性咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nlm"},{"pid":"5d285cc288fed804d16997e6b61e83fce5772183","tid":1123880,"uid":100016,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T18:00:48.000Z","msg":"明明食左咁多年蟲都冇事，點解睇完新聞爆出黎再食就會驚變有事，真係唔明"},{"pid":"24f530eaf0b0ebcd8438e9d93d214971e85cb062","tid":1123880,"uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b2d557b59a94e6dc4505db3790e3b1fed97dcad","tid":1123880,"uid":194606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:56:26.000Z","msg":"好似好理性咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nlm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T18:02:49.000Z","msg":"又冇發現活蟲，又冇講邊類線蟲 (線蟲只係一個種/目)。豬肉牛肉都有啵，重點係邊種蟲，同埋係人體存活期 。只係幫大家分晰清楚件事，我自己就中意食熟嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff4f5f70ad8b721294ca52700fcb7aa7b076ca4","tid":1123880,"uid":9256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T18:04:04.000Z","msg":"唔好再吹捧ok?<br />\n陣間又多人返"},{"pid":"bb25a1e638a36eff370cf05e870f4b69c487054a","tid":1123880,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5d285cc288fed804d16997e6b61e83fce5772183","tid":1123880,"uid":100016,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T18:00:48.000Z","msg":"明明食左咁多年蟲都冇事，點解睇完新聞爆出黎再食就會驚變有事，真係唔明"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T18:05:26.000Z","msg":"舉多個例子，車厘子都有唔少蟲。我地應該以蟲 properties 去睇件事，唔係用蟲嘅 existence 去睇。"},{"pid":"64e46838799a875ba07ed72aca9a31c471ddef41","tid":1123880,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9ff4f5f70ad8b721294ca52700fcb7aa7b076ca4","tid":1123880,"uid":9256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T18:04:04.000Z","msg":"唔好再吹捧ok?<br />